    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a good start, but it's a bit too generic for our VIP clients. They need to know exactly how the service will change. Can you add a section comparing the current concierge service with the new one? Like, maybe highlight the specific types of complex, personalized itinerary planning that the current system excels at, just so they're aware of the difference in service style?",
